      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>lamb meatballs</strong> to the tray[s]</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until the vegetables are tender and the lamb is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Greek-style lamb meatball tray bake</strong></p>",
